\f2\fs24 \cf3 6\'a0
\f3\b0 \cf3 Now the gates of Jericho\'a0were securely barred because of the Israelites. No one went out and no one came in.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Question #1   What is securely barred in your world right now?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What is shut up and can\'92t be taken ahold of?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The interesting thing is God promised them this land!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Questions #2  -  Do you know the promises of God?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Tomorrow we\'92ll send out an email with some of them listed.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The tension is this \'96 Every promise has a problem!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 \super 2\'a0
\f1\b0 \cf3 \nosupersub Then the\'a0Lord\'a0said to Joshua, \'93See, I have delivered\'a0Jericho into your hands, along with its king and its fighting men.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s amazing how two people can see the same situation completely differently.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Where you see opposition\'85God see\'92s opportunity!  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some would look and see a secure fortress locked up with huge walls.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Others see a secure fortress locked up with huge walls\'85with terrified people inside.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Question #3:  How do you see the situation in front of you?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf2 Transition:  This is the moment that Joshua has been waiting for.  He\'92s been waiting for the words \'91Go\'92 and what he hears are specific instructions that don\'92t match any marching orders for war I\'92ve ever heard of.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf3 \'a0
\f0\b \cf3 \super 3\'a0
\f1\b0 \cf3 \nosupersub March around the city once with all the armed men. Do this for six days.\'a0
\f0\b \cf3 \super 4\'a0
\f1\b0 \cf3 \nosupersub Have seven priests carry trumpets of rams\'92 horns\'a0in front of the ark. On the seventh day, march around the city seven times, with the priests blowing the trumpets.\'a0
\f0\b \cf3 \super 5\'a0
\f1\b0 \cf3 \nosupersub When you hear them sound a long blast\'a0on the trumpets, have the whole army give a loud shout;\'a0then the wall of the city will collapse and the army will go up, everyone straight in.\'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If this was me\'85I would have said, \'93Um God, you realize this isn\'92t a concert right?\'94\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This feels more like marching band to me than it does battle!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God tells Joshua, \'93I want you to get all your men together\'85and go for a walk!\'94\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If it is me \'96 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m worried about the walls and God is worried about the walk.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m worried about the battle and God\'92s worried about my obedience.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We want to talk about Walls, God wants to talk about our Walk\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You worry about you and I\'92ll worry about your problem!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For God the journey is just as important as the destination\'85sometimes more.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God will not hold you accountable, for what you are not responsible!  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We are not called to bring about victory\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We are called to be obedient\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 \super 10\'a0
\f1\b0 \cf3 \nosupersub But Joshua had commanded the army, \'93Do not give a war cry, do not raise your voices, do not say a word until the day I tell you to shout. Then shout!\'94\'a0
\f0\b \cf3 \super 11\'a0
\f1\b0 \cf3 \nosupersub So he had the ark of the\'a0Lord\'a0carried around the city, circling it once. Then the army returned to camp and spent the night there.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is the easiest battle plan ever to follow\'85walk in a circle for a week and then move straight forward.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Yet, I believe sometimes in life the easiest things can sometimes be the hardest to follow.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can you imagine how boring that must have been?  Monotonous?  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Don\'92t stop on lap 6\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Don\'92t stop on lap 10\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Don\'92t stop of 12\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is working in you and around you!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For some of you the struggle is you don\'92t know how many laps you\'92re suppose to take though!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf3 \super 20\'a0
\f1\b0 \cf3 \nosupersub When the trumpets sounded,\'a0the army shouted, and at the sound of the trumpet, when the men gave a loud shout,\'a0the wall collapsed; so everyone charged straight in, and they took the city.\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Easiest battle plan ever\'85yet maybe one of the hardest to do.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Take a walk and everything will be ok.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
