\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 YOU\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This summer we\'92re spending time focusing on our walk.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I believe as a church we\'92re going to continue to do great things and this is just the beginning.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But we\'92re in a season where God is calling us to focus on our walk.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Lift This Summer \'96 Sign up online!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf5 Illustration of me understanding how the reason we look at the walls so much is because we\'92re not walking and when we\'92re not walking we don\'92t have to watch where we\'92re going\'85I believe this is the trick of the enemy and how sometimes we end up in places we don\'92t want to\'85because we aren\'92t \'91watching\'92 where we are going.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
