\fs36 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\fs18 \cf3 \super 13\'a0
\f5\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Now when Joshua was near Jericho, he looked up and saw a man\'a0standing in front of him with a drawn sword\'a0in his hand. Joshua went up to him and asked, \'93Are you for us or for our enemies?\'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I believe this is the question today so many of us are asking God if we are honest with ourselves. \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God are you with me?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I know the type of girl I\'92m suppose to marry\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I know the job I\'92m suppose to get\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I know how this is all suppose to work out\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Where are you at in this whole situation?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Are you with me?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 14\'a0
\f5\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Neither,\'94 he replied, \'93but as commander of the army of the\'a0Lord\'a0I have now come.\'94 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I love this\'85Jesus says Joshua, let me explain something to you\'85You\'92re a part of my army, I\'92m not a part of yours!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We need to come to the place in our walk with God where we realize it is about us being a part of His army, not the other way around.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Then Joshua fell facedown\'a0to the ground\'a0in reverence, and asked him, \'93What message does my Lord\'a0have for his servant?\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The question I believe God is asking us is this \'96 are we for Him?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is the question we all have to answer and answer today!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus is for us \'96 already settled 2000 years ago when He came to earth to live a sinless life for you and me because we couldn\'92t do that.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Died on a cross and then was raised 3 days later into heaven where He waits to come back for you and me\'85IF!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And this is where we come in\'85There is a big IF!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is for you!  Are you for Him!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Have you come under His authority.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When Joshua realizes He is in the presence of God he goes from commander of his army to servant of God.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
